    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h1",
          "text": "Alibaba Achieves 37% Faster Financial Closings With Power BI Reporting"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "An optimized Power BI solution transforming Alibaba’s financial operations and generating timely and accurate month-end closings for over 100,000 brands and 30 million shoppers."
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [
        {
          "text": "OPTIMIZE VENDOR SETTLEMENTS",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
      "images": [
        {
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/daraz-header-graphic.png",
          "alt": null,
          "w": 685,
          "h": 531
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "headings": [],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Home » Power BI Financial Reporting For Online Marketplace"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "2012 - Pakistan"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Ecommerce"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Over 10,000 employees"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Alibaba"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "About The Client",
        "Daraz is the leading e-commerce platform across South Asia. After their advent as an online fashion retailer in 2012, they quickly expanded their business portfolio to a comprehensive online marketplace by 2015 and in 2018, they made a big move by becoming part of Alibaba’s expansive global footprint that enabled them to utilize Alibaba’s expertise in technology, logistics, and digital payments. Today, their platform proudly house 30 million active shoppers, supporting transactions for more than 200,000 active sellers and over 100,000 branded/non-branded products to sell."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": [
        {
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/alibaba-reb6f6fzc4hlu2h7ade0aw7bjk4loalc3at220tols.webp",
          "alt": "alibaba",
          "w": 200,
          "h": 200
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Navigating Data At Scale"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "The massive volume and complexity of data led to performance issues within their reporting infrastructure"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Difficulty generating critical financial reports in a timely manner, slowing down operations"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Their old method of reporting struggled to ensure the accuracy of financial reports, leading to ambiguous insights"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Achieving smooth and precise month end financial closings became a mess and time-consuming process"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "With 1000s of suppliers and shoppers to serve and products to sell, Alibaba's processes a continuous flow of financial data in terms of transactions, vendor settlements, and their outstanding balances, which seemed difficult with massive datasets in place."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [
        {
          "text": "OVERCOME ECOMMERCE DATA CHALLENGES",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "OUR SOLUTION"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Optimized Power BI Reporting"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Folio3 partnered with Alibaba to build a high-performance reporting solution using Microsoft Power BI. The approach was mainly focused on implementing advanced performance optimization techniques catering Alibaba’s large and complex dataset environment. The key aspects of our solution were:"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Deep Data Model"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Advanced DAX Query Tuning"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Strategic Data Integration"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "We designed Alibaba’s Power BI data models to cater huge data volumes efficiently, reducing redundant calculations and boosting data retrieval speeds.",
        "Our Power BI experts refined Data Analysis Expressions (DAX) queries, turning complicated calculations into highly efficient formulas that processed data faster with more reliability.",
        "We optimized data integration from Alibaba’s various data source systems to Power BI to maintain data integrity and freshness."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [
        {
          "text": "EXPLORE OUR ECOMMERCE DATA SOLUTIONS",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Business Outcomes"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Expedited Financial Closings"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "<img width=\"101\" height=\"101\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/achieve-dynamic-scalability-icon.svg\" alt=\" \"> Expedited Financial Closings"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Enhanced Reporting Accuracy"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "<img width=\"100\" height=\"101\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/32-Fewer-Human-Errors.svg\" alt=\" \"> Enhanced Reporting Accuracy"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Scalable Reporting Foundation"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "<img width=\"79\" height=\"81\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/extract-transform-icon.svg\" alt=\" \">Scalable Reporting Foundation"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "The implementation of Folio3's high-impact Power BI reporting solution delivered measurable benefits supporting Alibaba’s financial operations and large marketplace ecosystem:"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [
        {
